1-Form Based Authentication
    with username and password
    standard in most websites
    can logout
    HTTPS recommended

client POST username & pass, server validates and returns OK + Cookie SESSION_ID
and then every request from client to server is done thru SESSION_ID and
now server validates SESSION_ID ---- (by default expires after 30 mins of inactivity)

2-Basic Auth
    Authorzation: Basic JDSKFGSJB4et5435kdfsf==rgd
    HTTPS recommended
    cant logout
    simple and fast

--------------------------
Remember me cookie (2 weeks default)
it contains
    username,
    expiration time,
    md5 hash of the above 2 values
